        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.安装插件npm install hexo-asset-image –save</p><p>2.修改主_config.yml配置</p><p><img src="/2021/08/24/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/01-16297758930222.png" alt="1"></p><p>3.修改hexo-asset-image(位于themes下)</p><p><img src="/2021/08/24/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/2.png" alt="2"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
